HeliosX-Logger-Syslog version 1.00
==================================

HeliosX::Logger::Syslog extends the Helios::Logger class to allow 
Helios applications to log messages to syslogd. 


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Helios 2.30 or later
  Sys::Syslog 0.23


